Package: psycho
Type: Package
Title: The psycho Package: an Efficient and Publishing-oriented Workflow for Psychological Science
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Dominique", "Makowski", email="dom.makowski@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Dominique Makowski <dom.makowski@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/neuropsychology/psycho.R
BugReports: https://github.com/neuropsychology/psycho.R/issues
Description: The psycho package provides useful tools for psychologists, neuropsychologists and neuroscientists. It implements methods to create report-ready statistical outputs, as well as various convenient statistical functions used in psychological science.
